description:
This is a 23 minute workout called '20 min FULL BODY DUMBBELL WORKOUT | Sculpt and Strengthen | With Warm Up + Cool Down' from the channel fitbymik.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Join me for a 20 minute FULL BODY DUMBBELL EXPRESS WORKOUT. I've included a super quick warm up and cool down in this one for a complete routine to do on its own. Today I'll be using two 10LB dumbbells. This is a low impact routine which means there is NO JUMPING. There are NO REPEATS with intervals of 45 seconds on and 15 seconds rest.
